headline: Cocoa Volatility And Inflation Are Pressuring Mondelez Down To Intrinsic Value
summary: Despite short-term challenges, I estimate Mondelez's stock to bottom out at $69B in 2025, with a recovery to $88B by year-end. Explore more details here.
